lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur have taken a different path to Manchester City but manager Mauricio Pochettino believes the Londoners can soon rival Sunday's opponents as one of the world's biggest clubs.

headline.print_headline: Tottenham Project Can Take Us to the Top, Says Pochettino
